305 in Scottish football|1904\u201305]], [[1951\u201352 in Scottish football|1951\u201352]], [[1956\u201357 in Scottish football|1956\u20131957]], [[1961\u201362 in Scottish football|1961\u201362]], [[1972\u201373 in Scottish football|1972\u201373]]\n**''Runners-up'' (4): [[1903\u201304 in Scottish football|1903\u201304]], [[1905\u201306 in Scottish football|1905\u201306]], [[1925\u201326 in Scottish football|1925\u201326]], [[1963\u201364 in Scottish football|1963\u201364]]\n*[[Scottish Football League First Division|SFL First Division]] (Level 2)\n**''Runners-up'': [[2002\u201303 in Scottish football|2002\u201303]], [[2003\u201304 in Scottish football|2003\u201304]]\n*[[Scottish Football League Second Division|SFL Second Division]] (Level 3)\n**'''Winners''' (4): [[1977\u201378 in Scottish football|1977\u201378]], [[1981\u201382 in Scottish football|1981\u201382]], [[1992\u201393 in Scottish football|1992\u201393]], [[1999\u20132000 in Scottish football|1999\u20132000]]\n*[[Scottish League Two|SPFL League Two]] (Level 4)\n**''Runners-up/Play-off Winners'': [[2018\u201319 in Scottish football|2018\u201319]]\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Cup===\n*[[Scottish Cup]]\n**'''Winners''': [[1938\u201339 Scottish Cup|1938\u201339]], [[1954\u201355 Scottish Cup|1954\u201355]], [[1957\u201358 Scottish Cup|1957\u201358]]\n**''Runners-up'': [[1909\u201310 Scottish Cup|1909\u201310]], [[1911\u201312 Scottish Cup|1911\u201312]], [[1948\u201349 Scottish Cup|1948\u201349]]\n*'[[Scottish Challenge Cup]]\n**Runners-up: [[2006 Scottish Challenge Cup Final|2006\u201307]]\n{{col-end}}\n\n===Minor trophies===\n[[Image:ClydeEKCup.JPG|thumb|Clyde lift the Tommy McGrane Trophy in 2006]] \n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! style=\"background:#ffffff; colour:#000000;\"|Honour\n! style=\"background:#ffffff; colour:#000000;\"|Winners\n! style=\"background:#ffffff; colour:#000000;\"|Runners-up\n|-\n|[[Anglo-Franco-British Friendship Cup|Anglo-French Friendship Cup]]||[[Anglo-Franco-British Friendship Cup#1960-61|1961